---
layout: base.njk
title: Reading
description: Myles Lewando's bookshelf, by year
---

<h2>{{ title }}</h2>
<p>The audiobooks, ebooks, paperbacks, and hardbacks I've read each year, as of 2024. I tend to prefer physical books and I avoid ebooks and <a href="https://libro.fm/referral?rf_code=lfm227162">audiobooks</a> with DRM, where possible.</p>
<ul>
{% for book in books %}
  <li class="card">
    <img class="greyscale" src="{{ book.cover.src }}" width="{{ book.cover.width / 2 }}" height="{{ book.cover.height / 2 }}" alt="{{ book.cover.alt }}" />
    <p>
      <strong>{{ book.title }}</strong>
     by 
    {% for entity in book.author %}
      {% if book.author.length > 1 %}
        {% if entity === book.author[book.author.length - 1] %}
          {{ entity }}
        {% else %}
          {{ entity }}, 
        {% endif %}
      {% else %}
        {{ entity }}
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
    </p>
    <div class="metadata-container">
      <div class="metadata">{{ book.dateRead}}</div>
    </div>
  </li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
